name: Bacon Dangle Earrings
description:
Yes, you too can wear bacon from your ears!

These crispy bacon earrings are my very own illustrations. They are printed on thick plastic and hand-cut. The backs of the earrings are solid white.

The earrings are coated with several layers of non-toxic sealant to protect the color. However, in order to preserve the life your jewelry, I would not recommend wearing them in the shower or swimming pool.

Earrings are approx. 5.1cm (2 inches) long. They are hung on silver plated earring wires and jump rings.

I gift wrap all orders. All purchases come with a free gift!

name: Crafty Necklace
description:
A cream tattoo inspired banner clearly states "Crafty" with bright blue and green thread, blue and pink buttons and gray scissors tucked behind it. This is the perfect necklace for that fun, crafty lady in your life!

This colorful, bold pendant is an original graphic design handmade entirely by me. You will not find this design anywhere else. The pendant is printed on thick plastic and hand-cut.

It is coated with several layers of non-toxic sealant to protect the color and give it a bit of shine. However, in order to preserve the life of your jewelry, I would not recommend wearing it in the shower or swimming pool.

Pendant is 3.2 cm (1.25") wide and 5.1 cm (2") tall. Silver-toned ball chain is approx. 55.9 cm (24") long but can be adjusted to fit your size. There is a small lobster clasp at the end of the chain.

I gift wrap all orders. All purchases come with a free gift!

name: Sparrow "Love Always" Necklace
description:
This purple, pink and black sparrow is a tattoo-inspired original design. A golden banner waves around the sparrow and clearly states "Love Always".

The pendant is printed on thick plastic and hand-cut. It is coated with several layers of non-toxic sealant to protect the color. However, in order to preserve the life of your jewelry, I would not recommend wearing it in the shower or swimming pool.

Pendant is approx. 5.1 cm (2") long and 3.8 cm (1.5") tall. It is hung on a silver-toned ball chain that is approx. 55.9 cm (24") long. The chain can be lengthened or shortened upon request for free. There is a lobster clasp at the end of the chain.

I do gift wrapping upon request. All purchases come with a free gift!
